How it flows

IMAGE_TAG = v1.2.3
        │
        ▼
FULL_IMAGE = 111111111111.dkr.ecr.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/myapp:v1.2.3
        │
        ├── docker build -t ...myapp:v1.2.3
        ├── docker push  ...myapp:v1.2.3
        └── sed IMAGE_PLACEHOLDER → ...myapp:v1.2.3
